title: Ep 34: T. Dangle
description:
Today's proceedings:  A sister who keeps taking a dog, an interesting method of disinfecting,  and a boyfriend who doesn't want to stop drinking tea.  We also come up with a few interesting pen names for mother of the pod, including but not limited to: T. Dangle.  

Rate and Review our podcast and share it with your friends!
